'''2015年环西自行车赛'''是第70届[[环西自行车赛|环西自行车赛]]，于2015年8月22日至9月13日进行，此次比赛是2015年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/cycling/news/15264/9639217/cycling-final-stage-of-tour-of-spain-returns-to-madrid-after-break-from-tradition-in-2014|title=Vuelta a Espana: Final stage returns to Madrid after break from tradition in 2014|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2015-01-11|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929121059/https://www.skysports.com/more-sports/cycling/news/15264/9639217/cycling-final-stage-of-tour-of-spain-returns-to-madrid-after-break-from-tradition-in-2014|archivedate=2020-09-29}}</ref>。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[马贝拉|马贝拉]]附近的[[Puerto_Banús|Puerto Banús]]，终点位于[[马德里|马德里]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lavuelta.com/la-vuelta/2015/us/overall-route.html|title=2015 Route|work=Vuelta a España|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819125102/http://www.lavuelta.com/la-vuelta/2015/us/overall-route.html|archivedate=2015-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

共有22支车队参加此次比赛，其中17支车队为世界职业车队，另外5支车队则为洲际职业车队<ref name="vn-wild">{{cite news|title=Vuelta a España invites teams for 2015 race|url=http://velonews.competitor.com/2015/03/news/vuelta-espana-invites-teams-2015-race_364097|accessdate=2015-08-20|work=VeloNews|date=2015-03-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423014640/http://velonews.competitor.com/2015/03/news/vuelta-espana-invites-teams-2015-race_364097|archivedate=2015-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终来自阿斯塔纳车队的[[Fabio_Aru|Fabio Aru]]获得该届比赛的总冠军，这是他的首个环西自行车赛总冠军<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/sports/endurance/story/_/id/13647684/fabio-aru-wins-spanish-vuelta-1st-major-victory|title=Italian Fabio Aru wins Spanish Vuelta for 1st major victory|publisher=ESPN|date=2015-09-14|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200929121316/https://www.espn.com/sports/endurance/story/_/id/13647684/fabio-aru-wins-spanish-vuelta-1st-major-victory|archivedate=2020-09-29}}</ref>。来自Katusha车队的[[Joaquim_Rodríguez|Joaquim Rodríguez]]以57秒之差位列总排行榜第二名，除此之外他还获得了象征全能王的白衫。来自京科夫-盛宝车队的[[拉法乌·马伊卡|拉法乌·马伊卡]]则获得第三名。<ref name=cn-s21-report>{{cite news|title=Vuelta a España: Degenkolb wins final stage in Madrid|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/races/vuelta-a-espana-2015/stage-21/results/|accessdate=2015-09-29|work=Cyclingnews.com|date=2015-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161126212032/http://www.cyclingnews.com/races/vuelta-a-espana-2015/stage-21/results/|archivedate=2016-11-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>

